transcript.sentence: A sign reads midtown science high school behind its students walk around a crowded quad.
A high school gym, a basketball team practices.
The ball is passed.
A kid attempts a layup, but the ball is smacked out of his hand as he jumps.
He falls onto the floor while another kid stands over him.
The ball rolls away, knocking over bucket of paint on to assign. Another student is painting.
She stands up.
Peter parker looks over his shoulder at the argument.
The ball is passed back to flash.
And He returns to the game.
Peter walks over to the girl.
He returns the paint bucket up, right?
Flash blocks, another basket, and the ball flies towards the girl again.
Peter leans on one foot and catches it with amazing reflexes. The girl looks surprised.
Flash motions for peter to pass the ball.
Peter, thanks.
peter, hans, his camera to the girl. He steps onto the court.
Flash laughs.
uh.
They meet together in the middle of the court.
Flash goes to grab the ball, but peter moves it away faster.
Flash tries to grab it again.
Peter moves it around his back and holds it out with one hand.
Flash runs to it.
Peter jumps and swings it around, flashes head,
flash spins around, following the ball.
While his back is turned, peter bounces the ball off, flashes back and catches it again.
Flash turns around.
Peter smiles.
Peter swings the ball of flash as if to throw it again.
Flash ducks away, then stands up again.
Peter holds one hand over his eyes.
Peter turns his head away.
Flash goes to grab the ball with one hand and tries to pull out of peter's grip. He can't.
He tries to pull it with both hands and still can't.
Flash leaves the ball and backs away several steps.
Peter began stripling.
Peter runs to flash.
Flash collide with peter and gets knocked to the floor.
Peter jumps 10 feet across the gym towards the basket.
The girl whose paint got knocked over is still watching.
He soars closer to the basket with the ball above his head, ready to dunk.
A cheerleader watches as she blows a bubble with gum.
Peter dunks the ball and shatters the glass behind the basket. The cheerleader pops are gum.
Glass falls on peter as he lands
the hoop disconnected from the basket, lands on the floor.
Flash looks up from the floor.
Peter looks up slowly.
